
'''= A Hackbase or Hackerbase is a Live-in Hackerspace - a hackerspace with an in-house capacity for hacking & coliving.'''

URL = http://hackerspaces.org/wiki/Hackbase

=Characteristics=

* everything you would expect from a hackerspace + life support (sleep, eat)
* hosts hacker Residencies and Exchanges
* short or long-term stays
* promote a full-time sustainable hacker lifestyle, with minimal money needed
* extends on the practices of sharing already present in hackerspaces

(http://hackerspaces.org/wiki/Hackbase)


